### Attributes

Attribute       | Type    | Description
----------------|---------|------------
value           | string  | Mandatory. Depending on the type, format may change. Check the available types above"
field-type      | string  | Read only. Tells of which type the picked-custom-field is.
custom-field-id | Integer | Read only. Id of related custom field
owner-id        | Integer | Read only. Id of related owner of the polymorphic relationship
owner-type      | string  | Read only. Type of owner. Available types are: `candidate`

### Relations

Relation       | Description
---------------|------------
custom_field   | Mandatory. The custom field related to this resource.
owner          | Mandatory. Owner of the polymorphic relation. For now, the only acceptable owner is "candidate"
